data.description: Best of all worlds! Frankenmuth schools, Birch Run mailing/taxes, beautifully updated ranch. Modern White kitchen, all appliances to stay, including an electric and gas oven for the family chef. Hardwood and tile throughout, Sunroom to enjoy your beautiful yard with playscape. Newer septic, finished basement with an additional room that can be used for a home office. Minutes away from everything Frankenmuth has to offer.
